title: Buckethead/ Cobra Strike II - Y, Y+B, X+Y
description:
Cobra Strike II - Y, Y+B, X+Y is the second album by Buckethead &#039;side project&#039; of Cobra Strike. In addition to Buckethead, this album features a completely different cast of musicians. The music is more or less in the same vein as 13th Scroll.
